settings.description: Mario embarks on a journey in the Amazon jungle and that jungle is in massive destruction so Mario is going to explore the jungle
Welcome to my first level, I hope you enjoy this level that I have made, some A coins are hidden and E coin is locked, good luck getting all of them. =D

Mario traverses through the 4 elements of Water, Earth, Fire, and Air! Water room is a bit buggy!
Difficulty: 2/5

Caves... filled with bats and moles! don't forget the iconic buzzy beetles as well!

shame there's no cave ceiling tiles though.
The original tittle was "The little nipper inferno" but idk why I change the name,the e-coin represents the face of a nipper and the muncher's stem,i think is one of the worst e-coins i made.
When were there so many pipes in the sky? Who knows, but for whatever reason Mario needs to get through all the piranhas and koopas.
A nasty short showcasing the unpredictability of chain chomps.  see if you make make it through!
